hat he called a \\\"pretty big crash\\\" in training on Saturday, and though he rode in qualifying two days later, was then rested against the Danes.\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1992, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a \\\"pretty big crash\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 1882}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 1895}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 1907}, {\"ngram\": \"the Danes\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 1991}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has experience of sorts of an Olympic final already: having been told by British Cycling that his twin careers as rider and engineer did not fit the programme, he offered his services in the latter field to Denmark in Tokyo, where they won silver, before returning to a more accommodating home fold.\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2295, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2069, \"end\": 2084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Cycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\"}, {\"begin\": 2214, \"end\": 2219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.6071423831541016, \"rank\": 0.6464311858891304, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"experience\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2010}, {\"ngram\": \"sorts\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2019}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic final\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2039}, {\"ngram\": \"his twin careers\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2106}, {\"ngram\": \"rider\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2115}, {\"ngram\": \"engineer\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2128}, {\"ngram\": \"the programme\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2154}, {\"ngram\": \"his services\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2179}, {\"ngram\": \"the latter field\", \"from\": 2183, \"to\": 2199}, {\"ngram